- Terlalu lewatkah?

710
00:54:35,638 --> 00:54:37,390
Panggil saja tukang paip.

711
00:54:39,892 --> 00:54:42,561
Mungkin ia disebabkan oleh takungan air.

712
00:54:43,312 --> 00:54:45,815
- Saya cuba alirkan air dulu.
- Perlahan-lahan.

713
00:54:45,898 --> 00:54:47,274
Hati-hati, tekanan air tinggi…

714
00:54:47,358 --> 00:54:48,275
Oh, Tuhan.

715
00:54:49,276 --> 00:54:51,570
- Aduhai.
- Alamak.

716
00:54:51,654 --> 00:54:53,489
Oh, Tuhan!

717
00:54:58,244 --> 00:54:59,578
Tunggu.

