748
00:58:26,160 --> 00:58:27,244
Jadi?

749
00:58:32,791 --> 00:58:34,001
Mungkin sebaliknya.

750
00:58:36,337 --> 00:58:39,381
Bukan saya, tapi awak
yang memasuki kawasan saya.

751
00:58:41,634 --> 00:58:42,718
Sama seperti sekarang.

752
00:58:54,939 --> 00:58:57,358
