802
01:02:08,736 --> 01:02:10,696
Dah lewat, apa kata kita naik?

803
01:02:32,551 --> 01:02:34,178
Ini hadiah.

804
01:02:35,387 --> 01:02:38,182
Tentu awak nampak ia dah lama di koridor.

805
01:02:45,355 --> 01:02:47,524
"Tahniah kerana berpindah.
Daripada Ahn Ga-yeong."

806
01:02:47,608 --> 01:02:48,650
Itu…

807
01:02:56,617 --> 01:02:59,828
Saya tak tahu awak dah bercerai.

808
01:03:01,872 --> 01:03:04,291
Perceraian perkara serius
dan bukan satu kesalahan.

809
01:03:04,374 --> 01:03:05,709
Maaf saya pandang remeh.

810
01:03:09,546 --> 01:03:10,547
Apa?

811
01:03:10,631 --> 01:03:14,009
